      • parseJsonData

        private GetProducts.TopObject parseJsonData(android.util.JsonReader reader)
                                     throws java.io.IOException
        Decode the product info returned from the cloud. It contains some general information as well as the set of products included in the next "batch".
        Parameters:
        reader - JSON reader containing the JSON description of the products.
        Returns:
        returns the ArrayList of products, with each product represented by a ProductInfo instance. If there are no more products to be read, returns null.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - IOException can be thrown by the JsonReader instance.
